@Times Rita 

Ship is used by fans of a show, usually on online forums, to indicate who in the show they would like to see go ON A DATE.  Usage is "Oh, I'm totally shipping Jack and Diane - they'd make such a great couple!"  In extreme cases (read: all the time) warring factions can form of fans wanting different ships.  It's serious business. 

Comes from relationship.

